<problem id="fs-id1168047506784">
<para id="fs-id1168047150606">Describe the spectrum of each of the following:</para>
<list id="fs-id1168047342516" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
<item>starlight reflected by dust,</item>
<item>a star behind invisible interstellar gas, and</item>
<item>an emission nebula.</item>
